headline: United to Hold Webcast of Fourth-Quarter and Full-Year 2025 Financial Results
summary: United will hold a conference call to discuss fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 financial results on Wednesday, January 21 at 9:30 a.m. CT/10:30 a.m. ET.
